description:
Togame Momoko is a benevolent Magical Girl who saves inexperienced Magical Girls when they`re in a pinch.
As the middle child with two brothers, she grew up very assertive and outspoken, almost boyish. Despite that, she likes stuffed animals and other cute things. As a direct result of those preferences, she is also a fan of female idols.
Source: Official site
name: Togame Momoko
